  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prospective trial comparing the accuracy of [F-18]-FCH PET/MRI to US and 99mTc-MIBI
      SPECT/CT for pre-operative parathyroid localization in patients with primary
      hyperparathyroidism
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
